    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 游戏概述</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《记忆岛》是一款单人打造的2D像素RPG动作游戏，游戏中你将扮演一位在冒险旅途中意外失忆并来到“记忆岛”的普通人。在找回记忆的途中面对强大的敌人，解开地图中的谜题，了解岛上的人与事，体验一个个出色精彩的故事。在旅程中逐渐解开自己身份的真相，以及“记忆岛”的起源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250050/extras/c9a0d268b81d828638c80b03b4b3f80f.avif?t=1735892525\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250050/extras_big/c9a0d268b81d828638c80b03b4b3f80f.avif?t=1735892525 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 世界观介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一座神秘，奇幻，充满谜题的岛屿。但它貌似拥有将记忆变为现实的能力？你能感觉到你与它冥冥之中有某些奇怪的联系，这让你可以获得敌人的记忆并使用它们的招式与技能来保护自己。精通这些千奇百变的能力，找到合适且强力的搭配，面对凶险的强敌，保护想保护的人与事，建立自己与记忆岛的羁绊，创造属于你的冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250050/extras/f915b8d7884b9e23990ae0dc636eab91.poster.avif?t=1735892525\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250050/extras/f915b8d7884b9e23990ae0dc636eab91.webm?t=1735892525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250050/extras/f915b8d7884b9e23990ae0dc636eab91.mp4?t=1735892525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 玩法介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《记忆岛》是一款2D像素画风的RPG游戏，炼制药水，强化武器，获得技能，搭配护符，这类玩法都是《记忆岛》的核心。其次，《记忆岛》的重要目标是尽力讲好丰富的故事，让玩家在一款游戏中能有许多截然不同的情感体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250050/extras/ea3c970195d9ae392b8d1d6de9bb5607.poster.avif?t=1735892525\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250050/extras/ea3c970195d9ae392b8d1d6de9bb5607.webm?t=1735892525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250050/extras/b9e5301b0d2cd18326c9018ed435ef2b.poster.avif?t=1735892525\" width=800 height=570 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250050/extras/b9e5301b0d2cd18326c9018ed435ef2b.webm?t=1735892525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250050/extras/b9e5301b0d2cd18326c9018ed435ef2b.mp4?t=1735892525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >• 开发背景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《记忆岛》是由我购买各种素材网站上的资源，一个人坐在电脑前孤独打造的游戏。游戏发布后会保持更新，我在尽力做好每个环节，但精力十分有限。希望你在购买后能获得你想要的游戏体验，并留下你的宝贵建议，您的一切建议都是可接受的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
